Easily and securely keep track of all your Passwords!

AuthPass is a stand alone password manager with support for the popular Keepass (kdbx) format. Store your passwords, share across all your devices and easily find them whenever you need to login.

* All your passwords in one place.
* Generate secure random passwords for each of your accounts.
* Quick Unlock secured with biometric lock (android only right now)
* Keep track of your accounts across the web.
* App available for Mac, iOS,  Android and coming soon to Linux and Windows.
* Open Source available on https://github.com/authpass/authpass/